                        <interp inst="t18350921-1980-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 27.—
<rs id="t18350921-1980-punishment-49" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18350921-1980-punishment-49" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1980-18350921 t18350921-1980-punishment-49"></join>Transported for Ten Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Third Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
